data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home. Nestled in an established Sparks neighborhood, this residence offers the perfect combination of modern living and low-maintenance convenience. The kitchen is a chef's delight featuring lots of counter space, pantry and a sub-zero built in refrigerator. Hosting family or friends will be a delight with the open-flow from the kitchen to the great room. A wood burning fireplace really gives the room a great ambiance. There is a enclosed sunroom that is a great flex space for whatever your needs are. Primary bedroom is located on the main floor with the additional 3 bedrooms and a bathroom upstairs. Fridge, washer and dryer are included with no value or warranty. Come check this home out and make it your own! Buyer and buyers agent to verify all info.
